美国也有这一类的执法现象<ref name="ny">{{Cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2005-02/04/content_2545627.htm |title=美国式扫黄：警方“放蛇” 假戏真做 |access-date=2010-01-24 |archive-date=2009-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090602062319/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2005-02/04/content_2545627.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.hunantv.com/x/g/20091029/304710.html |title=纽约警方“放蛇”华商中招 卖酒给少年两华人被捕 |access-date=2010-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192136/http://news.hunantv.com/x/g/20091029/304710.html |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。如在网上装作未满14岁少女吸引恋童癖者，等待后者要求发生性关系<ref name="entrap">{{cite web | title = What is entrapment? | url = http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/explainer/1999/09/what_is_entrapment.html | publisher = http://www.slate.com | accessdate = 2012-02-14 | archive-date = 2018-10-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181002103536/http://www.slate.com/articles/news_and_politics/explainer/1999/09/what_is_entrapment.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，假扮不法交易商引出不法交易者<ref name="goo">{{cite web | title = Con Artist Starred in Sting That Cost Google Millions | url = http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204624204577176964003660658.html | publisher = http://online.wsj.com Online Wallstreet journal | accessdate = 2012-02-14 | archive-date = 2013-09-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130930043633/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052970204624204577176964003660658.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。美国法律规定，被“钓鱼”中套的一方只有在证明了以下三点后才能说明自身无过错：
